WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:05.999
Hey, good morning, family. Thank you for joining us again today. We're going to pray over your needs today.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.919
There are many of you, like this family right here, who are believing for so much.

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:22.651
We received that in the mail today, and I'm just like, 'Wow.'There are so many of you believing for a breakthrough for your loved ones.

00:00:22.652 --> 00:00:30.399
I mean, I have other photos right here. There are so many families. Like I said, we have photos now all over our car.

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:36.567
We drive around and look like we have photos everywhere that we pray over when we're driving around.

00:00:36.568 --> 00:00:47.279
People send them to us, and they need a breakthrough. These people are desperate; they need a touch from the Father.

00:00:47.280 --> 00:00:53.279
They don't need a stale word from a pastor where you go on a Wednesday night or a Sunday and you walk away thinking, 'What was that?

00:00:53.280 --> 00:01:06.559
Why did I waste my thirty minutes? Why did I waste an hour? I could have gotten more watching a YouTube video than I got from that.'I don't want to waste people's time.

00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:19.791
I say, 'God, we need a fresh river. We need fresh glory.'We need to get this old vinegar out of these old wineskins and put the anointing of the Holy Ghost on us.

00:01:19.792 --> 00:01:26.559
Rub that oil down into that pouch of who we are, that vessel, making it pliable again.

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:40.543
Because when you put that anointing oil on that vessel and rub it in, making that leather pouch pliable again, it makes it so if you put the new wine in it, it won't crack and bust.

00:01:40.544 --> 00:01:55.897
The oil and the anointing of the Holy Ghost is what makes us brand new every single day. You have to have that glory—the outward honey glow.

00:01:55.898 --> 00:02:06.559
That's why I told Diana—we talk about it all the time—I want it so much that it never turns off, that they have to put a drape around my head because people ask, 'What is going on with that dude's face?

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:16.479
He's glowing with the glory.'I tell my children, 'We represent the Father.'So, we act like the Father; we demonstrate ourselves as the Father would.

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:20.079
I know we're all a work in progress, but I'm just desperate for Him.

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:26.979
I'm desperate for Him. And I know what's coming. I know a great shaking is coming to awaken you.

00:02:26.980 --> 00:02:32.799
And I will sound the alarm, just like Jeremiah, to tell you all that God is coming.

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:38.799
And you have to get your house in order because we're running out of time.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:42.532
Thank God we're not like we were back then; we're under more grace.

00:02:42.533 --> 00:02:49.119
I get it, but I'm telling you all, a great shaking is coming. What's coming is not God's judgment.

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:55.999
Ladies and gentlemen, what's coming is not judgment; it's a Father correcting a child who is spoiled.

00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:11.839
It's the Father who is correcting a child who has gone wayward, saying, 'You've gone off the road, buddy, and I want you to come back over here in the fold.'The ninety-nine sheep are over here, and you're the one, and I'm trying to snatch that one.

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:17.999
There are a lot of ones, but He's trying to grab a hold of those ones.

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:23.119
And He's like, 'You got way off track, and you're fifty miles away from where you're supposed to be.

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:38.639
But I have more mercy and more love to let you have an extended time to bring them in.'Your unsaved loved ones—the people who are so wayward that you think, 'Man, they're never coming in.'No, all things are possible to him who believes.

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:43.779
Ladies and gentlemen, glory to God! All things are possible to him who believes.

00:03:43.780 --> 00:03:48.879
You've just got to believe it. You've got to put your faith into motion.

00:03:48.880 --> 00:03:53.039
What are you believing for today? You say, 'Well, I'm believing for finances.'Then sow a seed.

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:59.759
Every seed produces after its own kind. What are you believing God for today?

00:03:59.760 --> 00:04:00.579
David said, 'I give nothing that doesn't cost me something.

00:04:00.580 --> 00:04:11.599
If it doesn't cost you something, then it isn't precious to you.'And David gave when it hurt, and the Bible says that. And that's where I've tried to say, 'What's my chokehold?

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:24.624
Where am I at with the Lord concerning this?'People say, 'I don't believe in tithing because it's under the Old Covenant.'I believe in giving God something to work with.

00:04:24.625 --> 00:04:32.479
I believe in giving God—if the farmer sows a seed to reap a harvest, then I'm going to sow a seed to reap a harvest.

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:41.743
If I have a need, I sow a seed. That's what we always do in this household.

00:04:41.744 --> 00:04:45.919
Where do you give? You give to your local church. You give to where you're being fed spiritually.

00:04:45.920 --> 00:04:51.919
You give to the people who are pouring into you spiritually; that's where you give.

00:04:51.920 --> 00:04:58.470
So, where your pastor is and where the people are who are ministering to you on a day-to-day basis—those are the people you give to.

00:04:58.471 --> 00:05:09.599
Why? Because that's what keeps the local church going. If you don't have a local church in your area, you have to have a prayer covering.

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:16.929
That's what changes things. When that body comes together, you come as an army in that community. So, you keep that local church going.

00:05:16.930 --> 00:05:26.319
You keep the people who are feeding you going so that they keep feeding you, so they are able to distribute out and help others.

00:05:26.320 --> 00:05:30.612
It's like a storehouse. You bring your tithe to the storehouse.

00:05:30.613 --> 00:05:34.852
You bring that to the storehouse. Where the storehouse is, is where you're getting fed.

00:05:34.853 --> 00:05:38.479
That's where the grain is, and all the things you put in the storehouse.

00:05:38.480 --> 00:05:43.727
You bring the tithe to the storehouse. Your local church is your storehouse where you're getting fed.

00:05:43.728 --> 00:05:52.719
You take care of that pastor; you take care of them, and then you make sure they're able to have community outreach or whatever they're doing.

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:59.294
I just believe that that's what we do in these last days to help the local church out.

00:05:59.295 --> 00:06:03.048
We help it. You say, 'Well, we don't have to tithe.'No, but you still give.

00:06:03.049 --> 00:06:09.566
I don't believe there's a curse on people if you don't tithe, okay, but I believe that God said He rebukes the devourer for our sake.

00:06:09.567 --> 00:06:17.219
And if He did it back then, He'll do it again. And I want a blessing on my money.

00:06:17.220 --> 00:06:25.899
I want prosperity and His blessing on it—my heart hearing Him say, 'Brandon, well done, thou good and faithful servant.

00:06:25.900 --> 00:06:36.719
You did everything you could; you helped stretch the Kingdom of God throughout the whole world.'Most people don't want to give.

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:46.239
Most people are stingy with it, and they say, 'Well, when I get more money, I'll give and do this and that.'No, we started tithing because we had to.

00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:51.199
I don't know why I got off on this; I guess it's because Braden told me something.

00:06:51.200 --> 00:06:53.297
We get some emails where people say, 'We don't believe in tithing.

00:06:53.298 --> 00:06:59.471
What do you believe about it?'Well, this is my opinion: I believe in tithing. I believe in giving my ten percent.

00:06:59.472 --> 00:07:09.079
I believe in giving over the ten percent as much as I can because I know what it takes to get the gospel out. It seems like I've worked for churches my whole life.

00:07:09.080 --> 00:07:19.388
We knew what it took to get the bills paid at the church; we knew what it took to get the flyers out and all the staff paid. It takes millions of dollars.

00:07:19.389 --> 00:07:29.661
Most people say, 'Well, I gave my ten bucks.'Well, the church was thankful for the ten dollars, but there were a lot of tippers.

00:07:29.662 --> 00:07:37.839
You're believing that you can step into the overflow, for God to speak to you about abundant things, but that comes out of whether He can trust you with it.

00:07:37.840 --> 00:07:46.259
If God can't trust you with the ten percent that you have to tithe to Him, He's not going to show you the greater works.

00:07:46.260 --> 00:07:53.815
I'm telling you, I'm just being real with you all. I'm just telling you all the facts, and most people don't want to hear it.

00:07:53.816 --> 00:08:00.399
You say, 'Well, I'm qualified because I gave my five bucks to the Lord today.'You tipped God.

00:08:00.400 --> 00:08:05.839
You made a quarter of a million dollars last year, and you gave ten dollars. Whoop-de-do! I mean, I'm just saying.

00:08:05.840 --> 00:08:18.719
You think that you're qualified for God to tell you the secret things because you gave your hundred bucks and you made $250,000 last year? Seriously, it comes out of sacrifice.

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:34.079
David said, 'I didn't give God anything that didn't cost me something.'So you are expecting God to pour out his blessing on you in a dump truck load, but you gave in a thimble load.

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:43.631
And you're asking God to do something mightily in your finances whenever it's so backwards is what I'm trying to tell y'all.

00:08:43.632 --> 00:08:50.285
Seek ye first the kingdom and his righteousness, and all these things will be added unto you.

00:08:50.286 --> 00:08:58.099
Give, and it shall be given unto you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over will men give into your bosom. And so that's just what Diana and I believe.

00:08:58.100 --> 00:09:07.679
You ask us or tell you, I don't like talking about money stuff because you're like, 'Well, you know you're after money.'No, I don't care; I honest to goodness don't care.

00:09:07.680 --> 00:09:17.807
This is because people ask me, 'What do you believe about this, Brandon?'And this is what Diana and I believe. We believe in the power of the seed.

00:09:17.808 --> 00:09:24.399
We believe in the power that you give and it shall be given unto you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over will men give into your bosom.

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:29.703
That's what Diana and I believe. We believe that God is a rewarder of those that diligently seek Him.

00:09:29.704 --> 00:09:34.959
Not just with my time and prayer, but seeking Him with my finances.

00:09:34.960 --> 00:09:44.708
God, if I give, you said that you give me 30, 60, 100-fold. That's what you said in your word.

00:09:44.709 --> 00:09:51.431
You said in Malachi—I'm not putting myself underneath the old covenant, Lord—but you said back then that you rebuke the devourer for my sake.

00:09:51.432 --> 00:09:53.688
So Father, how much more will you rebuke the devourer for my sake now?

00:09:53.689 --> 00:10:00.052
I'm not underneath the old covenant, but I'm underneath the new, but I still want to believe in the blessing.

00:10:00.053 --> 00:10:06.026
I still want to believe in helping the church out. And it's a heart thing.

00:10:06.027 --> 00:10:12.586
It's a heart thing. And I say, 'God, my heart is for you. My heart is for the gospel.

00:10:12.587 --> 00:10:13.559
I want to help Billy Burke out. I want to help missionaries out.

00:10:13.560 --> 00:10:21.679
I want to help them.'If you're going out and praying for the sick and seeing people recover, I would like to help you.

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:24.824
If I see that you're doing something major for God, I want to help you.

00:10:24.825 --> 00:10:28.346
I see the cause, I see the anointing, and you sow into the anointing.

00:10:28.347 --> 00:10:33.279
Do you give all at one place? No, I split my seed a lot of times and I help each ministry out.

00:10:33.280 --> 00:10:39.679
I help pastors, prophets, teachers, evangelists, and all this.

00:10:39.680 --> 00:10:45.606
And I try, even if it's just five bucks whatever, until you grow. You say, 'Here, here, here.'But I try to sow the big one.

00:10:45.607 --> 00:10:51.510
And then the one that feeds me the most I give them the most, right, because I'm getting impartation from it.

00:10:51.511 --> 00:10:56.319
Above tithe I try to help out. So that's what I'm trying to say.

00:10:56.320 --> 00:11:05.039
And maybe that'll make sense for some of y'all, but you ask me my opinion, what Diana and I do. And that's exactly what we've done.

00:11:05.040 --> 00:11:20.319
And we've done it for a while now saying, 'God help me because I'm not going to be manipulated.''Well, all your tithe should come to my church because you're a part of my flock and you need to give all your money here.'Whatever I'm going to do, I'm going to do what the Holy Spirit tells me to do.

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:26.988
And people get ticked off about that, but whatever. I just follow the voice of the Lord for our life. And what he tells me to do is I give it.

00:11:26.989 --> 00:11:35.919
If you're not underneath the curse of the old covenant and it's not there, then I'm not going to be manipulated about my tithe either.

00:11:35.920 --> 00:11:40.319
I will not sit there and have you tell me all this stuff where I should be giving my money.

00:11:40.320 --> 00:11:46.079
I will follow the Holy Spirit and he will show me that which is to come.

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:51.039
And when you do that and you're led by the Holy Spirit you'll always be blessed.

00:11:51.040 --> 00:11:57.679
Follow the Holy Spirit in what the word tells you to do. Give to where you're being fed.

00:11:57.680 --> 00:12:07.199
Give to the ministries that are feeding you. And I'm telling you, God will anoint you. Be led by the spirit of God when it comes to your giving.

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:12.408
There's a lot of different theories; there's a lot of different theologies when it comes to this.

00:12:12.409 --> 00:12:14.079
And everybody's about it because everybody wants the money.

00:12:14.080 --> 00:12:17.919
And I'll be real with you, that's what I've seen a lot in the body of Christ.

00:12:17.920 --> 00:12:30.152
A lot of people want the money and they go, 'I feel that if you give this $58 seed and this $58 blessing you're going to get a miracle.'I don't get into all that stuff.

00:12:30.153 --> 00:12:32.159
I just give where I'm led to give to help when God tells me to give.

00:12:32.160 --> 00:12:41.999
And that's exactly what Diana and I do. And I am not manipulated by emotion.

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:47.459
Never give out of emotion. Give by the spirit of the Lord leading you.

00:12:47.460 --> 00:12:54.159
Does that make sense? If you're led by your emotions, your emotions change all the time.

00:12:54.160 --> 00:12:58.799
You can give a seed and you'll be like, 'Why in the world did I just give that?'five minutes later.

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:04.319
Sometimes it's the devil trying to torment you, but sometimes it is because you acted out in flesh.

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:17.599
And I'm not going to be, 'Well, you know, I heard the sob story about that and it was really sad at church and I gave it.'I'm not going to give out of emotion.

00:13:17.600 --> 00:13:19.519
I'm giving by the spirit of God leading me. Does that make sense?

00:13:19.520 --> 00:13:23.999
When you're led by the spirit of the Lord there is a blessing behind it.

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:31.679
But there truly is a 30, 60, and 100-fold. And you find the 100-fold grounds, you found a nugget.

00:13:31.680 --> 00:13:37.919
If you find the 60-fold, you still found a really good one. Thirty is okay; it's a return.

00:13:37.920 --> 00:13:44.159
But I'm serious, I told the Lord, I said, 'Where is the 100-fold ground?

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:51.903
Show me how to sow into that because I want to be the farmer that sows into the manure that gets back the big harvest.

00:13:51.904 --> 00:13:59.715
I sow to reap, I sow.'They said, 'Well, do you give to get?'Well, yeah, basically, but I'm not giving it out of that attitude.

00:13:59.716 --> 00:14:09.183
I'm giving to sow because God says he loves a cheerful giver, but he gives back 30, 60. It's his system.

00:14:09.184 --> 00:14:23.359
So I'm sowing into it saying, 'God, show me how to reap the maximum reward.'And if this is stony ground, run.

00:14:23.360 --> 00:14:27.679
'Well, their ministry died.'Well, it wasn't me, it's stony ground.

00:14:27.680 --> 00:14:32.243
It doesn't need to be there anyway. I mean, I'm just being real.

00:14:32.244 --> 00:14:40.143
Let them move on and do something else. Sell on eBay; it's a good living.

00:14:40.144 --> 00:14:44.039
If their ground is stony they shouldn't be in ministry anyway.

00:14:44.040 --> 00:14:53.209
If it's sandy soil and it's bad soil, why are they preaching then? Close the doors down and go on.

00:14:53.210 --> 00:14:56.326
We need people that are filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost in these last days.

00:14:56.327 --> 00:15:02.303
We don't need to be wasting people's time just doing it because it's all that I've ever known how to do.

00:15:02.304 --> 00:15:09.615
Do something else. Be a door greeter at Walmart. I mean, I don't mean to be rude but that's just real.

00:15:09.616 --> 00:15:17.199
Don't waste my time. And that's why I don't want to waste your time.

00:15:17.200 --> 00:15:23.439
We're just real. I've seen it all. I've been around some big ministers, some of the big guys.

00:15:23.440 --> 00:15:30.139
And you look at them and you go, 'What's real and what's not? Is there an anointing here or not?'I want you all to be successful.

00:15:30.140 --> 00:15:40.879
I want you to go from glory to glory and not keep going around the mountain expecting different results every single time. For 40 years they wandered in the wilderness.

00:15:40.880 --> 00:16:06.193
For 40 years they wandered and they never said, 'Why am I still going through what we're going through?''Moses, why are we still walking around this mountain?'And you go through another year and he's like, 'Well, the whole generation has to die because of unbelief and we're going to raise up the Joshuas and the Calebs to go and take the land because we really aren't the size of grasshoppers to these giants.'We're going to go and take the land.

00:16:06.194 --> 00:16:13.119
Who wants to be a land grabber? Us! I don't want to live in the valley of the shadow of death anymore.

00:16:13.120 --> 00:16:18.431
I want to live on the high peaks with Jesus Christ in these last days.

00:16:18.432 --> 00:16:21.789
I want to know how to go from glory to glory to glory. I'm so tired.

00:16:21.790 --> 00:16:35.486
You listen to all these sermons and you hear them and you know, is this really working? I want to see it. I want to see fruit.

00:16:35.487 --> 00:16:47.759
When your mom and dad and great-grandparents, and they all live from paycheck to paycheck and you give because they can preach the money out of your wallet and they get you all excited about it, and you walk away and you're still broke.

00:16:47.760 --> 00:16:57.599
You're still broke and it's frustrating and you go and you listen to it and you hear the prosperity gospel and you hear all this stuff.

00:16:57.600 --> 00:17:00.452
And God is a God that is abundantly rewarding those that diligently seek him.

00:17:00.453 --> 00:17:09.706
And he wants you to have 30, 60, and 100-fold, but you're giving it into bad ground. And you walk away going, 'What gives, Lord?

00:17:09.707 --> 00:17:15.549
How come you haven't met my stuff?'Because we're still looking for the mailbox mentality.

00:17:15.550 --> 00:17:24.151
We're looking for, "Well, God, where's my angel with the bag of money in his hand?"like that preacher talked about.

00:17:24.152 --> 00:17:28.675
I'm telling you that I've heard of miracles happening, and God does that, ladies and gentlemen.

00:17:28.676 --> 00:17:34.506
And God will do that; it's an exception, not the rule. He will anoint your hands to prosper.

00:17:34.507 --> 00:17:40.692
He will abundantly bless your hands to do something. Put your boat into motion.

00:17:40.693 --> 00:17:54.617
God isn't looking for the talents; you could either bury the talents, or you can make the talents work for you by doing something with your hands, asking Him for a creative idea to get wealth.

00:17:54.618 --> 00:17:58.575
"God, show me how to get this."I was the guy, I'm telling you, for a long time.

00:17:58.576 --> 00:18:23.327
As a janitor sitting back there, I was going, "Lord, Lord, teach me how some sister will walk up and give me $100 today because we're desperate for it."And that's a miracle for someone to hear it on their heart to give you some money, but God wants to make you a fisherman to go out and get it yourself.

00:18:23.328 --> 00:18:29.366
Teach me how to do it. And that's whenever the Lord told me, "Brennan, I'll teach you how to flip cars.

00:18:29.367 --> 00:18:56.101
Go out and buy this car that's broken over here, and pay your dad or whoever to put that timing belt on that car and fix it, and you can make it."I'm telling you, listen, I bought a car for, I think it was like 500 bucks—you weren't even born yet—and the Lord said, "Buy that car; it just needs a new timing belt on it and it's going to run."I bought it for 500 bucks and I sold it for $3,000.

00:18:56.102 --> 00:19:07.589
But at that time, that $500 seed for that car that needed a new timing belt—Of course, there was nothing else wrong with this car, and this was a long time ago—that $3,000 was a lot of money to us.

00:19:07.590 --> 00:19:14.079
So He said, "A man with a white shirt... after you fix this car, a man with a white shirt..."I prayed in the spirit.

00:19:14.080 --> 00:19:28.399
The Lord said, "A man with a white shirt is going to knock on your door tomorrow, and he's going to buy the car because the for-sale sign was on it."This Hispanic man walked up; he had a white shirt on just like the Lord said, and he said, "I've come to buy the car.

00:19:28.400 --> 00:19:38.719
I have cash."He gave me the cash. That's what I'm saying. This was back in 2002, 2003, somewhere around there.

00:19:38.720 --> 00:19:53.551
So, what I'm trying to say is just follow the voice of the Lord for your life, not looking for a mailbox mentality, but asking God to bless whatever you put your hands to and saying, "Lord, teach me.

00:19:53.552 --> 00:20:03.139
Teach me."That's just an example, but that's what we do still with eBay and Poshmark, asking God to give you an idea.

00:20:03.140 --> 00:20:16.045
The only reason I do what I do now is because I don't have much education; I just go, "Lord, teach me how to do this."And the Holy Spirit will lead you and guide you into everything.

00:20:16.046 --> 00:20:22.799
I just know there's a lot of people frustrated with preachers and teachers of the gospel.

00:20:22.800 --> 00:20:33.599
They're blessed, and people see it and they go, "Well..."because you get all these people bashing preachers that have everything and they go, "How come they have so much?"Well, you know, God's blessed them.

00:20:33.600 --> 00:20:44.589
They've sown their seed, they've reaped it. But it comes across—people become frustrated and critical over it and they go, "Where's mine?"Get out and do something with your harvest.

00:20:44.590 --> 00:20:49.839
Do something with your hands. Look for that supernatural idea.

00:20:49.840 --> 00:20:55.999
I believe in miracle money, but I don't believe in it the way everybody else believes in it like that.

00:20:56.000 --> 00:21:01.839
I believe God will anoint you to do something. He'll give you an idea.

00:21:01.840 --> 00:21:10.544
But there's a lot of it I believe that has been off, and a lot of the body of Christ is still believing 50 years later, and they're still living in the slums.

00:21:10.545 --> 00:21:28.101
And I've learned if you put your boat into motion and ask the Father, by seeking His face, for Him to anoint what you put your hands to, God will bless you.

00:21:28.102 --> 00:21:31.359
God will bless you with an idea. Believe for a promotion at your job.

00:21:31.360 --> 00:21:33.699
If you love your job and you want to stay there, then believe for a promotion.

00:21:33.700 --> 00:21:37.715
Some people go, "Well, I don't care if I ever have anything."Then fine, this message isn't for you.

00:21:37.716 --> 00:21:41.947
But there's a lot of people that are believing for a lot, and they're still doing the same thing.

00:21:41.948 --> 00:21:52.799
50 years later, they're still giving, they're still doing what they're doing, and they've sacrificed their whole life looking for the pot of gold at the end of the rainbow.

